cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR

This paper involves the use of deep learning techniques to generate virtual dual-energy images from standard radiographs. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves the use of adversarial networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of deep learning models for image processing and analysis also falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper involves the use of medical imaging, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR).
